title: Loyal Cubs fan cries during celebration [VIDEO]
text:
It was an emotional day for Cubs fans on Tuesday when their Cubbies closed out a postseason series at Wrigley Field for the first time.
Some cheered, some clapped, some yelled, “ YABOO!” For others, the moment moved them to tears. Watch this longtime Cubs fan’s reaction:
